&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*If you bought a year's subscription your account will be credited for that year&lt;/strong&gt;. Your entitled time will not increase until that entire year has passed and you sign up for another subscription (be that a 1 month, 3 month, or year plan).&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
